#31054
The Frjosa Hel-vegr Tundra~
   To the south, you can hear the loud roaring of the river.  The snow is very
deep and makes moving very difficult.  Everything is white and cold here.  
What a hopeless landscape the tundra can be.  You have exits in all four
cardinal directions all lead to more snow except the south.  
~
